        "authorId" : "ff334962-2ee8-45f1-ad4a-cfb65ffd6744",
        "body" : "It could probably be coerced to a Boolean, but the extra strictness is good IMO. Not that it matters much, but `windowsVerbatimArguments` isn't documented anyway, IIRC.\n",
        "createdAt" : "2016-11-16T15:30:25Z",
